C
RASTER MOSAICKING AND CLIPPING
Layer>Add Layer>Add Raster Layer
add photo/file>India 1,2,3,4
Go to Raster>Miscellaneous>Merge
In input layers select India 1/2/3/4
In merged select three dots>save to file 
Create new in 2C Merge_Files.tif
run deselect the other 4

Layer>Add Vector Layer>select IND_adm0.shp
then add border to it 
Raster>Extraction>Clip Raster by Mask layer
Input>Merge_Files
Advanced Parameters new file Clipped_File.tif
run
